nern« zwischen arbeitsmarktpolitischen Anforderungen und gleichstellungspolitischen Bestrebungen bewegt.  aMen in child care centers - about the recruitment of male preschool teachers in Germany and Sweden as a moment of discursive negotiation of gender relations.  afunded by Böckler  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aDiscourse analysiszGermany. 0aDiscourse analysiszSweden. 0aMale child care workerszGermany. 0aMale child care workerszSweden. 0aMasculinityzGermany. 0aMasculinityzSweden. 0aSex role in the work environmentzGermany. 0aSex role in the work environmentzSweden. 0aSex rolezGermany. 0aSex rolezSweden. 0aSexxGovernment policyzGermany. 0aSexxGovernment policyzSweden. 4aArbeitsmarktsegregation. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aCare. 4aDekonstruktivismus. 4aDeutschland. 4aDiskursanalyse. 4aEuropa. 4aGender Studies. 4aGeschlecht. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aMännliche Erzieher. 4aQueer Theory. 4aSchweden. 4aWohlfahrtsstaatsforschung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh  aCare.  aCultural Studies.  aDeconstructivism.  aDiscourse Analysis.  aEducational Research.  aEurope.  aGender.  aGermany.  aLabour Market Segregation.  aMale Educators.  aQueer Theory.  aSociety.  aSweden.  aWelfare State Research.2 aBöcklerefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2z978311076667708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839444320zCo-access D